### THE DIVISIONS OF THE DAY.

There are eight parts of the day: 1. morning; 2. dawn; 3.
vapourlessness; 4. noon; 5. evening; 6. twilight, &c.

Or thus:--

1\. Dawn; 2. morning; 3. vapourlessness; 4. noon; 5. rest; 6. twilight;
7. disappearance; 8. midnight <span
id="fr_417"></span>[1](bim1166.htm#fn_413.md).

